OL,3,C'More than 440,000 hours of sewage
OL,4,Creleased' along England's coastline in
OL,5,C2023
OL,7,FIt found there were 68,481 incidents
OL,8,Fof sewage released into England's seas
OL,9,Flast year, totalling 440,446 hours.
OL,11,FMore than a quarter of these, some
OL,12,F117,584 hours over 21,213 spills, were
OL,13,Fwithin 1.9 miles (3km) of a bathing
OL,14,Fspot, the assessment found.
OL,16,FThe analysis has been released as
OL,17,Fcomedian Nish Kumar fronts a new film
OL,18,Fwith Friends of the Earth, with a
OL,19,Fspoof news report on the opening of
OL,20,Ftourist attraction Sh*t Beach on a
OL,21,Fseaside town's sewage-ridden beach.
