OL,7,FIt identified Cowes Beach on the Isle
OL,8,Fof Wight as most affected, with nearly
OL,9,F5,000 hours of sewage released near
OL,10,Fthe bathing spot in 2023, followed by
OL,11,FMeadfoot in Torbay and Plymouth Hoe
OL,12,FWest.
OL,14,FThe comedian said: "Record-breaking
OL,15,Famounts of shit and pollution clogging
OL,16,Fup our rivers and seas is no joke.
