OL,5,C2023
OL,7,F"If we don't act now, we'll all be
OL,8,Fswapping our swimmers for hazmat suits
OL,9,Fand packing an E. coli testing kit
OL,10,Fbefore hitting the great British
OL,11,Fseaside this summer.
OL,13,F"We can't let water companies have the
OL,14,Flast laugh, as their shareholders
OL,15,Fpocket huge payouts while our bills
OL,16,Fincrease.
OL,18,F"We need to show that we give too much
OL,19,Fof a shit about our beaches and rivers
OL,20,Fto let them end up being a national
OL,21,Fhealth hazard."
