OL,7,FKierra Box, nature campaigner at
OL,8,FFriends of the Earth, said the film
OL,9,Fwas a spoof but "could be a taste of
OL,10,Fwhat's to come if the government
OL,11,Fdoesn't force water companies to clean
OL,12,Fup their act".
OL,14,F"We urgently need to enshrine the
OL,15,Fright to a healthy environment in UK
OL,16,Flaw, to give communities the power to
OL,17,Ftake back their local seas and
OL,18,Fbeaches, to hold polluters to account,
OL,19,Fand ensure this never happens again,"
OL,20,Fshe urged.
